<DATE>the twen|ty fir&s;t day of February in the year of our Lord one thou&s;and &s;even hundred and ninety five, and of the Common|wealth the nineteenth.</DATE></DATELINE>
<SIGNED> <HI>THOMAS MIFFLIN.</HI> By the Governor, JAMES TRIMBLE, Deputy Secretary.</SIGNED></CLOSER>
